Package: clustpro
Type: Package
Title: Guided Clustering Analysis and Interactive Visualization using 'shiny'
Version: 0.1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Christian D.","Peikert", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "christian.peikert@t-online.de"),
    person("Muhammad Numair", "Mansur", email = "numair.mansur@gmail.com", role = c("aut"))
    )
Maintainer: Christian D. Peikert <christian.peikert@t-online.de>
Description: Supports the common clustering algorithms k-means and c-means and enables optimal cluster size prediction. In addition to interactive visualization, it allows user-friendly analysis and sharing of data using 'JavaScript' and the 'shiny' framework.
